<i>Buterfly Fly Away]</i>

1055
01:18:21,129 --> 01:18:24,792
<i># You tucked me in, turned out the light</i>

1056
01:18:24,833 --> 01:18:28,394
<i># Kept me safe and sound at night</i>

1057
01:18:28,436 --> 01:18:32,873
<i># Litle girls depend</i>
<i>on things like that</i>

1058
01:18:35,410 --> 01:18:39,039
<i># Brushed my teeth and combed my hair</i>

1059
01:18:39,080 --> 01:18:42,243
<i># Had to drive me everywhere</i>

1060
01:18:42,283 --> 01:18:46,845
<i># You were always there</i>
