1061
01:18:48,823 --> 01:18:52,384
<i># You had to do it all alone</i>

1062
01:18:52,427 --> 01:18:56,659
<i># Make a living, make a home</i>

1063
01:18:56,698 --> 01:19:01,328
<i># It must have been</i>
