01:19:18,119 --> 01:19:21,611
<i># Caterpillar in the tree</i>

1069
01:19:21,656 --> 01:19:25,148
<i># How you wonder who you'll be</i>

1070
01:19:25,193 --> 01:19:29,323
<i># Can't go far, but you can always dream</i>

1071
01:19:32,333 --> 01:19:35,393
<i># Wish you may and wish you might</i>

1072
01:19:35,437 --> 01:19:39,066
<i># Don't you worry, hold on tight</i>

1073
01:19:39,107 --> 01:19:43,476
<i># I promise you there will come a day</i>

1074
01:19:44,779 --> 01:19:47,942
<i># Buterfly, fly away</i>

1075
01:19:53,621 --> 01:19:55,282
<i># Buterfly, fly away</i>

1076
01:19:55,323 --> 01:19:57,018
<i># Buterfly, fly away</i>

1077
01:19:57,058 --> 01:20:00,858
<i># You got your wings, now you can't stay</i>

1078
01:20:00,895 --> 01:20:05,127
<i># Take those dreams</i>
<i>and make them all come true</i>

1079
01:20:07,735 --> 01:20:13,196
<i># Buterfly, buterfly, buterfly</i>

1080
01:20:13,241 --> 01:20:15,869
<i># Buterfly, fly away #</i>

1081
01:20:50,912 --> 01:20:53,312
[chickens clucking]

1082
01:21:05,059 --> 01:21:06,754
- Miley!
- Yes! What?

1083
01:21:07,462 --> 01:21:08,929
Miley!

1084
01:21:09,864 --> 01:21:11,593
- Are you OK?
- Don't you know better

1085
01:21:11,633 --> 01:21:14,363
than to yell at someone asleep
on top of a chicken coop?

1086
01:21:14,402 --> 01:21:15,869
I do now.

1087
01:21:17,472 --> 01:21:20,464
Did you do this?
Were you out here all night?

1088
01:21:20,508 --> 01:21:22,066
Just a little hard work. That's all.

1089
01:21:24,112 --> 01:21:25,477
Life's a climb.

1090
01:21:31,219 --> 01:21:32,413
Is it time?

1091
01:21:33,922 --> 01:21:35,150
Yeah, it's time.

1092
01:21:36,324 --> 01:21:37,484
Let's go.

1093
01:21:38,760 --> 01:21:40,955
[Indistinct chattering]

1094
01:21:45,233 --> 01:21:46,791
Hey!

1095
01:21:46,834 --> 01:21:49,302
We received a
one-thousand-dollar contribution

1096
01:21:49,337 --> 01:21:52,033
- from an anonymous benefactor!
- We're getting there.

1097
01:21:52,073 --> 01:21:53,700
Oh, hey.

1098
01:21:53,741 --> 01:21:56,733
Isn't it awesome? This is terrific!
See you at the concert.

1099
01:21:56,778 --> 01:21:58,143
[Laughing]

1100
01:22:09,591 --> 01:22:11,582
[Classical music playing]

1101
01:22:11,626 --> 01:22:13,890
- Coming through. Coming through.
- Stay back!

1102
01:22:13,928 --> 01:22:16,863
I'm not the agent,
I'm not the manager, I'm the grandma.

1103
01:22:16,898 --> 01:22:19,458
- I'm the real deal.
- She's OK.

1104
01:22:24,472 --> 01:22:25,837
Have a good day, ma'am.

1105
01:22:27,075 --> 01:22:30,567
Whew, honey. I had no idea.

1106
01:22:30,612 --> 01:22:33,206
No wonder they hide you away
in this camper thingie.

1107
01:22:33,248 --> 01:22:35,842
Whoo! Oh!

1108
01:22:35,883 --> 01:22:37,714
Is it always this crazy?

1109
01:22:38,219 --> 01:22:39,618
Always.

1110
01:22:39,654 --> 01:22:44,819
Well, I know the getting here was hard,
but what you're doing is a good thing.

1111
01:22:44,859 --> 01:22:46,292
You should be proud of that.

1112
01:22:50,999 --> 01:22:52,364
I know I am.

1113
01:23:04,145 --> 01:23:05,544
This was my mom's?

1114
01:23:08,650 --> 01:23:09,742
Yeah.

1115
01:23:10,718 --> 01:23:12,743
She'd be proud of you too.

1116
01:23:15,723 --> 01:23:16,917
Yeah.

1117
01:23:20,061 --> 01:23:21,323
Thanks.

1118
01:23:22,730 --> 01:23:26,291
Um, I'm just gonna
put it in here so I can...

1119
01:23:26,334 --> 01:23:29,428
So I can have it in my pocket
with my show and everything.

1120
01:23:29,470 --> 01:23:31,370
That's good, close to you.

1121
01:23:32,707 --> 01:23:34,937
Thank you. I love you.

1122
01:23:35,910 --> 01:23:37,400
I love you, darling.

1123
01:24:02,770 --> 01:24:06,638
[Crowd] Hannah!
Hannah! Hannah! Hannah!

1124
01:24:17,051 --> 01:24:18,712
Ya! Ya!

1125
01:24:23,057 --> 01:24:25,423
[<i>#</i> Hannah Montana: <i>Rockstar]</i>

1126
01:24:25,460 --> 01:24:27,291
- Yeah!
- [Cheering]

1127
01:24:28,229 --> 01:24:29,753
Whoo!

1128
01:25:34,462 --> 01:25:35,827
I can't do this.

1129
01:25:37,064 --> 01:25:39,328
[All murmuring]

1130
01:25:42,537 --> 01:25:43,834
Sorry.

1131
01:25:52,580 --> 01:25:57,074
I've loved being Hannah, but I
just don't think I can do it anymore.

1132
01:25:59,053 --> 01:26:02,386
At least not here, not with you guys.

1133
01:26:03,357 --> 01:26:06,190
See, this is... this is home.

1134
01:26:09,163 --> 01:26:12,189
This is where I'm from. This is family.

1135
01:26:12,233 --> 01:26:15,327
And there's only so many sacrifices
you can ask a family to make.

1136
01:26:20,041 --> 01:26:22,601
The last time I stood
on this stage I was six.

1137
01:26:26,214 --> 01:26:27,511
I was...

1138
01:26:31,619 --> 01:26:32,984
I was just Miley.

1139
01:26:41,629 --> 01:26:42,960
And I still am.

1140
01:26:44,499 --> 01:26:46,933
[Crowd gasping]

1141
01:26:58,246 --> 01:26:59,440
Hi. It's...

1142
01:27:01,282 --> 01:27:02,306
It's me.

1143
01:27:10,358 --> 01:27:15,022
I've hurt a lot of people,
but... I didn't mean to.

1144
01:27:15,062 --> 01:27:18,498
And... if it's not too late...

1145
01:27:19,901 --> 01:27:21,732
...I sure would like
a second chance.

1146
01:27:35,049 --> 01:27:37,244
I know you all came
to hear Hannah, but...

1147
01:27:39,353 --> 01:27:41,821
...if you don't mind,
I've written y'all a song.

1148
01:27:41,856 --> 01:27:43,881
It's kind of personal.

1149
01:27:43,925 --> 01:27:47,258
It's about what I've learned
over the last couple weeks.

1150
01:27:50,498 --> 01:27:51,931
Life's a climb.

1151
01:27:55,570 --> 01:27:56,935
But the view is great.

1152
01:28:01,676 --> 01:28:05,373
[<i>#</i> Miley Cyrus: <i>The Climb</i>]

1153
01:31:41,428 --> 01:31:43,953
[Cheering]

1154
01:32:02,082 --> 01:32:06,519
- Whoo!
- Yeah. Whoo!

1155
01:32:22,169 --> 01:32:24,330
[Crowd silences]

1156
01:32:24,371 --> 01:32:26,202
Thanks for letting me live my Hannah.

1157
01:32:28,776 --> 01:32:29,936
Bye.

1158
01:32:30,945 --> 01:32:33,311
Please.

1159
01:32:33,347 --> 01:32:35,907
Please be Hannah.
We'll keep your secret.

1160
01:32:35,950 --> 01:32:38,077
[All laughing]

1161
01:32:39,587 --> 01:32:42,055
I'm sorry, I can't. It's too late.

1162
01:32:43,123 --> 01:32:44,181
Sure, you can!

1163
01:32:47,528 --> 01:32:51,191
Put the wig back on. You'll never
have a normal life if you don't!

1164
01:32:51,232 --> 01:32:53,860
Hannah's a part of you!
Don't let her go!

1165
01:32:53,901 --> 01:32:55,425
[Crowd shouting in agreement]

1166
01:32:55,469 --> 01:32:59,132
[Crowd] Hannah!
Hannah! Hannah! Hannah!

1167
01:33:24,899 --> 01:33:26,025
No, please.

1168
01:33:28,402 --> 01:33:31,064
- Somebody, stop him!
- [Man] Call security!

1169
01:33:34,108 --> 01:33:37,077
Watch it! One more step
and I hit "send."

1170
01:33:37,111 --> 01:33:39,136
- Don't do it.
- Sorry, nothing on Earth'll

1171
01:33:39,179 --> 01:33:41,477
- stop me from...
- [both] Daddy! Daddy! Daddy!

1172
01:33:41,515 --> 01:33:43,380
Phoebe, Clarissa, what are you doing?

1173
01:33:43,417 --> 01:33:46,784
This nice lady sorted it all out.
Two free tickets.

1174
01:33:46,820 --> 01:33:48,617
Upper class. It was brilliant!

1175
01:33:48,656 --> 01:33:51,591
I thought the girls'd appreciate
a couple of free tickets.

1176
01:33:51,625 --> 01:33:53,388
We too late?
She going to sing again?

