01:33:53,427 --> 01:33:55,793
I can't believe that
I'm only one degree away...

1178
01:33:55,829 --> 01:33:59,162
[crowd] Hannah! Hannah! Hannah!

1179
01:33:59,199 --> 01:34:01,724
- My gosh! It's Hannah Montana!
- It's really her!

1180
01:34:01,769 --> 01:34:03,760
- You're right there! I'm here!
- I can't believe it!

1181
01:34:03,804 --> 01:34:06,568
I really love you.
We're your biggest fans ever, really.

1182
01:34:06,607 --> 01:34:09,007
You're not going to destroy
their dreams, are you?

1183
01:34:09,043 --> 01:34:10,601
That's what Hannah's all about.

1184
01:34:11,879 --> 01:34:15,508
- Is that your story?
- I must be dreaming! Pinch me!

1185
01:34:15,549 --> 01:34:18,416
No, that's not my story.

1186
01:34:18,452 --> 01:34:21,046
- [Phoebe] Oh, my gosh!
- [Whistles] Girls!

1187
01:34:23,357 --> 01:34:26,053
- Get this down, Lucinda.
- <i>[Lucinda] Fire away, Ozzie.</i>

1188
01:34:26,093 --> 01:34:28,288
<i>Bon Chic</i> magazine

1189
01:34:28,329 --> 01:34:32,993
is run by a wretched, soulless succubus
who preys on the misfortune of others,

1190
01:34:33,033 --> 01:34:35,433
and I'm not going
to put up with it any longer!

1191
01:34:35,469 --> 01:34:37,369
<i>[Lucinda] Ozzie! Ozzie! Come...</i>

1192
01:34:37,404 --> 01:34:38,701
Think I just quit.

1193
01:34:41,542 --> 01:34:45,205
[Vita] Come on. Let's go out front.
I think Hannah's got more songs in her.

1194
01:34:45,245 --> 01:34:47,042
Thanks, partner.

1195
01:34:47,081 --> 01:34:49,242
- <i>[man] Everybody, stay where you are.</i>
- Miley!

1196
01:34:49,283 --> 01:34:52,013
<i>[Man] We got lots more music for you.</i>

1197
01:34:52,052 --> 01:34:55,385
Remember that crush I had
on you, and I said I was over it?

1198
01:34:55,422 --> 01:34:56,446
Yeah.

1199
01:34:58,258 --> 01:34:59,816
Uh...

1200
01:34:59,860 --> 01:35:01,088
Please jump.

1201
01:35:07,568 --> 01:35:08,933
So not over it.

1202
01:35:14,141 --> 01:35:16,166
Right on!

1203
01:35:16,210 --> 01:35:19,702
[<i>#</i> Hannah Montana: <i>You'll</i>
<i>Always Find Your Way Back Home</i>]

1204
01:36:31,718 --> 01:36:35,154
Hey.

1205
01:37:39,987 --> 01:37:42,114
[Cheering]

1206
01:37:42,156 --> 01:37:44,420
[<i>#</i> Miley Cyrus: <i>Hoedown Throwdown</i>]

1207
01:39:20,587 --> 01:39:22,748
- And cut it!
- [Applause]

1208
